{"tid":1700953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來寫遺書係好難","createTime":"2019-11-08T18:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T03:27:52.000Z","uid":80737,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b99738309ff57a6cad34584b1e52356385219b","tid":1700953,"uid":80737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:23:44.000Z","msg":"不知不覺就差不多半年啦 <br />\n我都知道革命唔係得個講字 所以我會自行升級武力<br />\n奈何朋友都只係和理飛 所以我都一直一個人發夢<br />\n一個人有好有唔好 但咬到就真係咁大<br />\n所以今日打算寫定個遺書 但拎起支筆先發覺個腦一片空白 咩都諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n我請問吓大家有冇遺書格式？<br />\n想同屋企人講好多野 但又怕太長應唔應該分開幾封寫？"},{"pid":"25726442803ad0830088fa022a8d81e76f83f94b","tid":1700953,"uid":36612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534e3822fdc45ff80737b946ddf704cba89968a9","tid":1700953,"uid":62167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"諗到咩就寫咩<br />\n唔會有老師捉你行文同格式<br />\n加上到時人都死左"},{"pid":"e5dbf9755272a2e5f19ede08690991e003a928a2","tid":1700953,"uid":80737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"534e3822fdc45ff80737b946ddf704cba89968a9","tid":1700953,"uid":62167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"諗到咩就寫咩<br />\n唔會有老師捉你行文同格式<br />\n加上到時人都死左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"好怕有咩講留咗 到底又冇得叫教主俾部iphone我用<br />\n佢咁小氣"},{"pid":"39cf99ad679b7e4b5dc17b495631d50f3fe9a320","tid":1700953,"uid":207084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:30:06.000Z","msg":"要煲底相見"},{"pid":"9d8550ba9c80d6681216777b3849e691c8c03879","tid":1700953,"uid":309118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打，我都試過寫，唔需要有格式，只係要將你呢刻想講低嘅嘢寫出嚟。"},{"pid":"41e77e84177373fad843b4ddecbecabae9e4ac02","tid":1700953,"ui